WEBVTT

00:02:59.323 --> 00:03:00.724
(Vicheko)

00:03:00.748 --> 00:03:02.260
Hivyo, kwa faida yangu,

00:03:02.272 --> 00:03:03.167
wangapi mnajitambua zaidi kama watoaji

00:03:03.247 --> 00:03:04.672
kuliko wapokeaji au wanaolipizaji?

00:03:04.892 --> 00:03:05.838
Inua mkono.

00:03:06.962 --> 00:03:09.911
OK, ingekuwa zaidi kabla kuongelea hizi takwimu.

00:03:10.525 --> 00:03:14.152
Lakini, kuna cha kushangaza
zaidi hapa,

00:03:14.176 --> 00:03:17.472
kwa sababu watoaji mara nyingi
hujitoa wenyewe,

00:03:17.496 --> 00:03:19.675
huyaboresha mashirika yao zaidi.

00:03:20.345 --> 00:03:23.112
Tuna ushahidi mwingi --

00:03:23.136 --> 00:03:26.869
tafiti nyingi kuhusu tabia za watoaji

00:03:26.893 --> 00:03:29.030
katika timu au shirika --

00:03:29.054 --> 00:03:32.140
na zaidi watu wanavyosaidiana, kufundisha